org.pircbotx.cap

Interface CapHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EnableCapHandler, SASLCapHandler, TLSCapHandler

    public interface CapHandler
    Generic CAP handler. Relevant handle methods are called when a CAP line is received. Connecting is not considered finished until a method returns true
    Author:
    Leon Blakey
